-AVL Trees:
AVL trees invented to overcome the drawbacks of the BT when it becomes imbalanaced.
As in only left node of root are filled, which behaves like a linked list and give O(n) instead of O(log n) for search,addition and deletion
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=jDM6_TnYIqE
-At most height of AVL tree=1.44 log n, if there are n nodes in the tree.
-Time to search/insert/delete-O(logn)
-https://www.geeksforgeeks.org/practice-questions-height-balancedavl-tree/

-Red Black Tree:
To avoid the frequent rotations performed on AVL trees, Red-Blac trees are used.